        			$(this).watermark($(this).attr('data-watermark'), { useNative: false,className: 'watermark'});
        			// watermarkDescriptionTextValue[$(this).attr("id")]
        		}
        	)
        	// DD-roudies
            DD_roundies.addRule('.panel, .panel .timing, .download_boxes .premium, #login_area, .comparison .plan, .file_control, .file_control .toolbar, .dialog, .tips_message, .comparison, .payout_table, .money_signup, .news_box, .my_earnings .payable, .dashboard .account .acc_table, .manager_alert, .premium_extend, .join_box, .dialog_choose_plan, ul.highlight', '6px', true);
            DD_roundies.addRule('.file_manager .file_control', '6px 6px 0 0', true);
            DD_roundies.addRule('.file_manager .file_control .toolbar', '6px 6px 0 0', true);


			// Toggle Signup Form
			$('.step1').click(function(){
				$('#loginMsg').hide();
				$(this).hide();
				$('.step2').slideDown(300)
			})
			
			
			
		
			

        })
    
    </script>

<script>

	$(document).ready(function(){
		$('#login').mouseenter(function(){
			$('#login_area').show();
		});
		$('#no_sign').click(function(){
			 $("#login_area").hide();
		});
		
		$('#partner_payment_type2').change(onSelectChange);
		$('#partner_email2').keypress(onSelectChange);
		
		function onSelectChange(){
			var selected = $("#partner_payment_type2 option:selected");
			var regexp = selected.attr('rel');

			jQuery.validator.addMethod("patternCheck", function(value, element) {
				var re = new RegExp(regexp);
				return re.test(value);
		    }, jQuery.format("Invalid payment account"));

			$('#promoForm #partner_email2').focus();
		}
		
		var promoFormValidator = $('#promoForm').validate({
			errorElement: 'span',
	        errorClass: 'fail_info',
	        errorPlacement: function(error, element){
	        	$('#promoError').html(error);
	            //$(error).insertAfter(element.next());
	        },
	        success: function(label){
	            label.remove();
	        },
	        rules: {
	            partner_email2:{
	                required: true,
	                patternCheck: true
	            }
	        },
	        messages: {
	            partner_email2:{
	                required: "Provide your payment account",
		            patternCheck: "Invalid payment account"
	            }
	        }
		});
		
		$('#sys_clock .lang_select').bind('mouseenter mouseleave', function() {
			$('div:eq(0)', this).slideToggle(150);
			$(this).toggleClass('hover');
	        num = $(this).hasClass('hover') ? $('a', this).size() : 1;
			$(this).stop(true, false).animate({ height: num * ($('a', this).height()+2) },200);
        });

	});
	function displayOverlayDialog(layerId) {
		window.scroll(0,0);
		//$('#upgrade_btn').attr('disabled', true);
		$('#middle_panel').fadeTo('slow', 0.5);
		$('.middle').fadeTo('slow', 0.5);
		$('#' + layerId).show();
	}

	function hideOverlayDialog(layerId) {
		$('#' + layerId).hide();
		//$('#upgrade_btn').attr('disabled', false);
		$('#middle_panel').fadeTo('slow', 1);
		$('.middle').fadeTo('slow', 1);
	}
	
	function changeLocale(locale) {
    	$("#localeForm [name=locale]").val(locale);
    	$("#localeForm").submit();
	};

	initClock('April  1, 2016 16:57:32', 'dynamic_clock');
</script>

Shining Moment'</a></h1><p>The 30th edition of "One Shining Moment" will be marked by Luther Vandross' version at the close of the NCAA tournament on TBS, while Ne-Yo's version will air on TNT and Tru-TV.</p></div>

								<a href="mailto:?subject=Festus Ezeli: A 'pretty good' prank&body=http://es.pn/236CHUR" data-route="false" class="btn-social sm email icon-font-before icon-email-solid-before Module"></a>
							</li>
						
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
			<span class="category">NBA</span>&nbsp;<span class="timestamp" data-time="2016-04-01T19:35:14Z" data-behavior="date_ago"></span>

		function loadDefer(){
			if( !deferLoaded ){
				var deferScripts = ['http://a.espncdn.com/redesign/0.294.13/js/espn-defer.js', 'http://a.espncdn.com/redesign/0.294.13/js/espn-defer-low.js'];

				    document.getElementsByTagName('head')[0].appendChild(script);
				}
			    deferLoaded = true;
			}
		}

	var focus_data = [
		{
		'img': 'http://www-img.oss-cn-qingdao.aliyuncs.com/www.cnzz.com/www%E8%BD%AE%E6%92%ADbanner/%23273d7-ccnzz-%E9%A6%96%E9%A1%B5%EF%BC%8D1000-386.jpg',
		'title': 'ãåçÂ·ç¼åä¿¡.ç½ç»æ°æ®Â·CNZZæå¼ºç»ä¹ãå±åå¼å¯âåç+âæ¶ä»£ï¼',
		'bgcolor': '#273d7c',

		{

			'url': 'http://gxb.cnzz.com',

        {
			'img': 'http://www-img.oss-cn-qingdao.aliyuncs.com/www.cnzz.com/www%E8%BD%AE%E6%92%ADbanner/lADOC1othM0Bgs0D6A_1000_386.jpg',
			'title': 'åç+',
			'bgcolor': '#0c1d2e',
			'url': 'http://ubdc2016.umeng.com/',
			'target': '_blank'
		},
        {
            'img': 'http://www-img.oss-cn-qingdao.aliyuncs.com/www.cnzz.com/www%E8%BD%AE%E6%92%ADbanner/3333331000-386-%2357099e.jpg',
            'title': 'é¿éäº',
            'bgcolor': '#57099e',
            'url': 'http://click.aliyun.com/m/4213/',
            'target': '_blank'
        },
        
	
     ];

	(function(win, doc) {
		win = win || window;
		doc = doc || document;
		var o = {},
			d = {};
		o.focus = {
			'box': doc.getElementById('focus'),
			'main': doc.getElementById('focus_main'),
			'arrow': doc.getElementById('focus_arrow'),
			'dot': doc.getElementById('focus_dot'),
			'mainBox': [],
			'dotLi': []
		};
		o.scroll = doc.getElementById('scroll');
		o.countLogin = doc.getElementById('count_login');
		//o.count = doc.getElementById('count');

		d.focus = {
			'active': 0,
			'target': 0,
			'timer': '0.5s',
			'autoTimer': '3000'
		};
		d.timer = {};

		function focus() {
			//ç¦ç¹å¾ å¤§å¾
			var _focus = doc.createDocumentFragment();
			//ç¦ç¹å¾ ç¹
			var _dot = doc.createDocumentFragment();
			for (var i = 0; i < focus_data.length; i++) {
				var _mainBox = doc.createElement('div');
				_mainBox.className = 'focus_main_box';
				_mainBox.style.transitionDuration = d.focus.timer;
				_mainBox.style.transitionTimingFunction = 'linear';
				_mainBox.style.transitionProperty = 'opacity';
				_mainBox.style.backgroundColor = focus_data[i].bgcolor;
				_mainBox.innerHTML = '<div class="wrap"><a href="' + focus_data[i].url + '" title="' + focus_data[i].title + '" target="' + focus_data[i].target + '"><img src="' + focus_data[i].img + '" alt="' + focus_data[i].title + '" /></a></div>';
				_focus.appendChild(_mainBox);
				o.focus.mainBox.push(_mainBox);
				var _dotLi = doc.createElement('li');
				i == 0 && (_dotLi.className = 'active');
				_dot.appendChild(_dotLi);
				o.focus.dotLi.push(_dotLi);
			};
			o.focus.main.innerHTML = '';
			o.focus.main.appendChild(_focus);
			o.focus.dot.appendChild(_dot);
			//ç¹å»å·¦å³ç®­å¤´
			o.focus.arrowLeft = o.focus.arrow.getElementsByTagName('b')[0];
			o.focus.arrowLeft.onclick = function() {
				clearInterval(d.focus.auto);
				showFocusPrev();
			};
			//ç¹å»å·¦å³ç®­å¤´
			o.focus.arrowRight = o.focus.arrow.getElementsByTagName('i')[0];
			o.focus.arrowRight.onclick = function() {
				clearInterval(d.focus.auto);
				showFocusNext();
			};
			//ç¹å» ç¹
			for (var i = 0; i < o.focus.dotLi.length; i++) {
				o.focus.dotLi[i].index = i;
				o.focus.dotLi[i].onclick = function() {
					d.focus.target = this.index;
					clearInterval(d.focus.auto);
					showFocus();
				};
			};
			o.focus.box.onmouseenter = function() {
				clearInterval(d.focus.auto);
			};
			o.focus.box.onmouseleave = autoFocus;
			//èªå¨
			autoFocus();
		};
		//åä¸å¸§
		function showFocusPrev() {
			if (d.focus.target == 0) {
				d.focus.target = focus_data.length - 1;
			} else {
				d.focus.target--;
			};
			showFocus();
		};
		//åä¸å¸§
		function showFocusNext() {
			if (d.focus.target == focus_data.length - 1) {
				d.focus.target = 0
			} else {
				d.focus.target++;
			};
			showFocus();
		};
		//ç¦ç¹å¾è¿å¨
		function showFocus() {
			if (getSys().ie && getSys().ie <= 9) {
				clearInterval(d.focus.opacityTimer);
				var _filter = 0;
				d.focus.opacityTimer = setInterval(function() {
					_filter += 5;
					_filter > 100 && (_filter = 100);
					o.focus.mainBox[d.focus.target].style.filter = 'alpha(opacity=' + _filter + ')';
					o.focus.mainBox[d.focus.active].style.filter = 'alpha(opacity=' + (100 - _filter) + ')';
					o.focus.mainBox[d.focus.target].style.zIndex = 2;
					o.focus.mainBox[d.focus.active].style.zIndex = 1;
					if (_filter == 100) {
						d.focus.active = d.focus.target;
						clearInterval(d.focus.opacityTimer);
					};
				}, 20);
			} else {
				o.focus.mainBox[d.focus.target].style.zIndex = 2;
				o.focus.mainBox[d.focus.active].style.zIndex = 1;
				o.focus.mainBox[d.focus.target].style.opacity = 1;
				o.focus.mainBox[d.focus.active].style.opacity = 0;
				d.focus.active = d.focus.target;
			};
			for (var i = 0; i < o.focus.dotLi.length; i++) {
				if (i == d.focus.target) {
					o.focus.dotLi[i].className = 'active';
				} else {
					o.focus.dotLi[i].className = '';
				};
			};
		};
		//èªå¨è¿è¡
		function autoFocus() {
			d.focus.auto = setInterval(showFocusNext, d.focus.autoTimer);
		};

		//èµ°é©¬ç¯
		var slider = function(set) {
			this.set = set || {};
			this.init();
		};
		slider.prototype = {
			'init': function() {
				this.o = this.set.o;
				this.arrow = getClass(this.o, 'slider_arrow')[0];
				this.box = getClass(this.o, 'slider_box')[0];
				//éæ°æåºå¾æ 
				this.reBuilt();
				this.inn = getClass(this.o, 'slider_inn');
				this.length = this.inn.length;
				this.max = Math.ceil(this.length - this.set.per);
				//æ¯å¦æ»¡è¶³æ»å¨æ¡ä»¶
				if (this.inn.length <= this.set.per) {
					this.arrow.style.display = 'none';
				} else {
					this.page = 0;
					this.arrowClick();
					//èªå¨è¿è¡
					this.autoRun();
					var _self = this;
					this.o.onmouseover = function() {
						clearInterval(_self.auto);
					};
					this.o.onmouseout = function() {
						_self.autoRun();
					};
				};
			},
			'reBuilt': function() {
				var _link = getClass(this.box, 'link_inn');
				var _link_html = '';
				for (var i = 0; i < _link.length; i++) {
					if (i % 2 == 0) {
						_link_html += '<div class="slider_inn">';
					};
					_link_html += '<div class="link_inn">' + _link[i].innerHTML + '</div>';
					if (i % 2 == 1) {
						_link_html += '</div>';
					};
				};
				this.box.innerHTML = _link_html;
			},
			'createClone': function() {
				var _self = this;
				//åç½®
				var _next = doc.createDocumentFragment();
				//åç½®
				var _prev = doc.createDocumentFragment();
				for (var i = 0; i < this.set.per; i++) {
					var _tmpNext = doc.createElement('div');
					_tmpNext.className = this.inn[i].className;
					_tmpNext.innerHTML = this.inn[i].innerHTML;
					_tmpNext.style.cssText = this.inn[i].style.cssText;
					_next.appendChild(_tmpNext);

					var _tmpPrev = doc.createElement('div');
					_tmpPrev.className = this.inn[this.inn.length - i - 1].className;
					_tmpPrev.innerHTML = this.inn[this.inn.length - i - 1].innerHTML;
					_tmpPrev.style.cssText = this.inn[this.inn.length - i - 1].style.cssText;
					//_prev.insertBefore(_tmpPrev, _prev.childNodes[0]);
					this.box.insertBefore(_tmpPrev, this.inn[0]);
				};
				//this.box.insertBefore(_prev, this.inn[0]);
				this.box.appendChild(_next);
				//ä½ç½®
				this.box.style.marginLeft = '-' + (this.set.width * this.set.per) + 'px';
				//é¡µç 
				this.page = 1;
			},
			'arrowClick': function() {
				var _self = this;
				var _b = this.arrow.getElementsByTagName('b');
				_b[0].onclick = function() {
					_self.slidePrev();
				};
				_b[1].onclick = function() {
					_self.slideNext();
				};
			},
			'slidePrev': function() {
				clearInterval(this.timer);
				if (this.page == 0) {
					this.box.insertBefore(this.inn[this.length - 1], this.inn[0]);
					this.box.style.marginLeft = (0 - this.set.width) + 'px';
				} else {
					this.page--;
				};
				this.slideTo(1);
			},
			'slideNext': function() {
				clearInterval(this.timer);
				if (this.page == this.max) {
					this.box.appendChild(this.inn[0]);
					this.box.style.marginLeft = '-' + (this.set.width * (this.length - this.set.per - 1)) + 'px';
				} else {
					this.page++;
				};
				this.slideTo();
			},
			'slideTo': function(a) {
				var _self = this;
				var _target = 0 - this.set.width * this.page;
				this.timer = setInterval(function() {
					var _left = parseInt(_self.box.style.marginLeft) || 0;
					var _distant = (_target - _left) / 10;
					_distant = a ? Math.ceil(_distant) : Math.floor(_distant);
					_self.box.style.marginLeft = (_left + _distant) + 'px';
					if (_left == _target) {
						clearInterval(_self.timer);
					};
				}, 10);

			},
			autoRun: function() {
				var _self = this;
				this.auto = setInterval(function() {
					_self.slideNext();
				}, 5000);
			}
		};
		//æ»å¨æé®
		document.getElementById('product_service_button').onclick=o.countLogin.onclick = o.scroll.onclick = function() {
			windowScrollTop();
		};

		function windowScrollTop() {
			var _timer = setInterval(function() {
				var _top = doc.documentElement.scrollTop || doc.body.scrollTop;
				_top = Math.ceil(_top * 0.8);
				if (_top < 10) {
					_top = 0;
					clearInterval(_timer);
				};
				win.scrollTo(0, _top);
			}, 20);
		};
		//é¡µé¢æ»å¨
		addEvent(win, 'scroll', countPosition);
		addEvent(win, 'load', countPosition);

		function countPosition() {
			var _top = doc.documentElement.scrollTop || doc.body.scrollTop;
			if (_top > 400) {
				clearTimeout(d.timer.scroll);
				o.scroll.style.display = 'block';
				d.timer.scroll = setTimeout(function() {
					o.scroll.style.opacity = '0.1';
				}, 100);
				document.body.className = 'fixed';
			} else if (_top < 136) {
				clearTimeout(d.timer.scroll);
				o.scroll.style.opacity = 0;
				d.timer.scroll = setTimeout(function() {
					o.scroll.style.display = 'none'
				}, 100);
				document.body.className = '';
			};
		};
		//æµè§å¨çæ¬
		function getSys() {
			var Sys = {};
			var ua = navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase();
			var s;
			(s = ua.match(/msie ([\d.]+)/)) ? Sys.ie = s[1]: (s = ua.match(/firefox\/([\d.]+)/)) ? Sys.firefox = s[1] : (s = ua.match(/chrome\/([\d.]+)/)) ? Sys.chrome = s[1] : (s = ua.match(/opera.([\d.]+)/)) ? Sys.opera = s[1] : (s = ua.match(/version\/([\d.]+).*safari/)) ? Sys.safari = s[1] : 0;
			return Sys;
		};
		//className
		function getClass(o, ClassName, tag) {
			if (!o) {
				return [];
			};
			if (document.getElementsByClassName) {
				return o.getElementsByClassName(ClassName);
			} else {
				tag = tag || '*';
				var r = new RegExp('\\b' + ClassName + '\\b');
				var a = new Array();
				var t = o.getElementsByTagName(tag);
				for (i = 0; i < t.length; i++) {
					if (r.test(t[i].className)) {
						a.push(t[i]);
					};
				};
				return a;
			};
		};
		//ç»å®å¨ä½
		function addEvent(Elem, type, handle, boo) {
			if (Elem.addEventListener) {
				var _boo = boo ? true : false;
				Elem.addEventListener(type, handle, _boo);
			} else if (Elem.attachEvent) {
				Elem.attachEvent("on" + type, handle);
			};
		};
		//
		focus();
		//æ é´éæ»å¨
		//æåæ¡ä¾
		/*
			new slider({
				'o': doc.getElementById('customer'),
				'per': 3,
				'width': 960,
				'blank': 1
			});
		*/


		new slider({
			'o': doc.getElementById('link'),
			'per': 8,
			'width': 120
		});

	})(window, document);

if(document.getElementById("noticeScroll")){
	var scrollup = new ScrollText("noticeScroll");
	scrollup.LineHeight = 24;        //åææå­æ»å¨çé«åº¦
	scrollup.Amount = 1;            //æ³¨æ:å­æ¨¡å(LineHeight)ä¸å®è¦è½æ´é¤Amount.
	scrollup.Delay = 20;           //å»¶æ¶
	scrollup.Start();             //æå­èªå¨æ»å¨
	scrollup.Direction = "up";   //é»è®¤è®¾ç½®ä¸ºæå­åä¸æ»å¨
}		
$(function(){
	$(window).on('scroll',function(){
		var st = $(document).scrollTop();
		if( st>0 ){
			if( $('#content').length != 0  ){
				var w = $(window).width(),mw = $('#content').width();
				if( (w-mw)/2 > 70 )
					$('#gotop').css({'left':(w-mw)/2+mw+20});
				else{
					$('#gotop').css({'left':'auto'});
				}
			}
			$('#gotop').fadeIn(function(){
				$(this).removeClass('hide');
			});
		}else{
			$('#gotop').fadeOut(function(){
				$(this).addClass('hide');
			});
		}	
	});
	$('#gotop .go').on('click',function(){
		$('html,body').animate({'scrollTop':0},500);
	});

	$('#gotop .cz-weixin').hover(function(){
		$('#gotop .cz-weixin-con').removeClass('hide');
	},function(){
		$('#gotop .cz-weixin-con').addClass('hide');
	});
});

	</script>

if(document.getElementById("noticeScroll")){
	var scrollup = new ScrollText("noticeScroll");
	scrollup.LineHeight = 24;        //åææå­æ»å¨çé«åº¦
	scrollup.Amount = 1;            //æ³¨æ:å­æ¨¡å(LineHeight)ä¸å®è¦è½æ´é¤Amount.
	scrollup.Delay = 20;           //å»¶æ¶
	scrollup.Start();             //æå­èªå¨æ»å¨
	scrollup.Direction = "up";   //é»è®¤è®¾ç½®ä¸ºæå­åä¸æ»å¨
}		
$(function(){
	$(window).on('scroll',function(){
		var st = $(document).scrollTop();
		if( st>0 ){
			if( $('#content').length != 0  ){
				var w = $(window).width(),mw = $('#content').width();
				if( (w-mw)/2 > 70 )
					$('#gotop').css({'left':(w-mw)/2+mw+20});
				else{
					$('#gotop').css({'left':'auto'});
				}
			}
			$('#gotop').fadeIn(function(){
				$(this).removeClass('hide');
			});
		}else{
			$('#gotop').fadeOut(function(){
				$(this).addClass('hide');
			});
		}	
	});
	$('#gotop .go').on('click',function(){
		$('html,body').animate({'scrollTop':0},500);
	});

	$('#gotop .cz-weixin').hover(function(){
		$('#gotop .cz-weixin-con').removeClass('hide');
	},function(){
		$('#gotop .cz-weixin-con').addClass('hide');
	});
});

	</script>

    var reCAPTCHA_publickey='6LdSvrkSAAAAAOIwNj-IY-Q-p90hQrLinRIpZBPi';
    
	    function showCaptcha() {
		      var RecaptchaOptions = {
		          theme: 'custom',
		          lang: 'en',
		          custom_theme_widget: 'recaptcha_widget'
		      };
		      Recaptcha.create(reCAPTCHA_publickey,
		          "captchaArea", RecaptchaOptions);
  		}
            
        $(document).ready(function() {
        	$('#submitButton').click(function(){
				if($('#userIAgree').attr('checked')){
					if (!$('#regForm').valid()){
	        			return;
			   		}
					$.ajax({
					  url: 'signup.php',
					  type: 'POST',
					  dataType: 'json',
					  data: 'collectorRegFormSubmit='+$('#collectorRegFormSubmit').val()+'&ajaxSignUp='+$('#ajaxSignUp').val()+'&userName='+$('#userName').val()+'&userPassword='+$('#userPassword').val()+'&userConfirmPassword='+$('#userConfirmPassword').val()+'&userEmail='+$('#userEmail').val()+'&userPremVoucherCode='+$('#userPremVoucherCode').val()+'&userIAgree='+$('#userIAgree').val()+'&recaptcha_response_field='+$('#recaptcha_response_field').val()+"&recaptcha_challenge_field="+$('#recaptcha_challenge_field').val(),
					  success: function(data){
					  if (data['success']!=null){
					  	self.location="dashboard.php";
					  }else{
					  	$('span.fail_info').hide();
					  	for(var key in data){
					  		var errorMsgElementId = key+'ErrorMsg';
					  		$('#'+errorMsgElementId).html(data[key]);
					  		$('#'+errorMsgElementId).show();
					  	}
					  	Recaptcha.reload();
					  }
					  }
					});
				}else{
					alert('You must check the box below to indicated that you have read and agree to the terms of use.');
					return false;
				}
			}
			);
        	
        	
        	$('.placeholder').each(
        		function(){
        		if($(this).attr('data-watermark'))
        			$(this).watermark($(this).attr('data-watermark'), { useNative: false,className: 'watermark'});
        			// watermarkDescriptionTextValue[$(this).attr("id")]
        		}
        	)
        	// DD-roudies
            DD_roundies.addRule('.panel, .panel .timing, .download_boxes .premium, #login_area, .comparison .plan, .file_control, .file_control .toolbar, .dialog, .tips_message, .comparison, .payout_table, .money_signup, .news_box, .my_earnings .payable, .dashboard .account .acc_table, .manager_alert, .premium_extend, .join_box, .dialog_choose_plan, ul.highlight', '6px', true);
            DD_roundies.addRule('.file_manager .file_control', '6px 6px 0 0', true);
            DD_roundies.addRule('.file_manager .file_control .toolbar', '6px 6px 0 0', true);


			// Toggle Signup Form
			$('.step1').click(function(){
				$('#loginMsg').hide();
				$(this).hide();
				$('.step2').slideDown(300)
			})
			
			
			
		
			

        })

<script>

	$(document).ready(function(){
		$('#login').mouseenter(function(){
			$('#login_area').show();
		});
		$('#no_sign').click(function(){
			 $("#login_area").hide();
		});
		
		$('#partner_payment_type2').change(onSelectChange);
		$('#partner_email2').keypress(onSelectChange);
		
		function onSelectChange(){
			var selected = $("#partner_payment_type2 option:selected");
			var regexp = selected.attr('rel');

			jQuery.validator.addMethod("patternCheck", function(value, element) {
				var re = new RegExp(regexp);
				return re.test(value);
		    }, jQuery.format("Invalid payment account"));

			$('#promoForm #partner_email2').focus();
		}
		
		var promoFormValidator = $('#promoForm').validate({
			errorElement: 'span',
	        errorClass: 'fail_info',
	        errorPlacement: function(error, element){
	        	$('#promoError').html(error);
	            //$(error).insertAfter(element.next());
	        },
	        success: function(label){
	            label.remove();
	        },
	        rules: {
	            partner_email2:{
	                required: true,
	                patternCheck: true
	            }
	        },
	        messages: {
	            partner_email2:{
	                required: "Provide your payment account",
		            patternCheck: "Invalid payment account"
	            }
	        }
		});
		
		$('#sys_clock .lang_select').bind('mouseenter mouseleave', function() {
			$('div:eq(0)', this).slideToggle(150);
			$(this).toggleClass('hover');
	        num = $(this).hasClass('hover') ? $('a', this).size() : 1;
			$(this).stop(true, false).animate({ height: num * ($('a', this).height()+2) },200);
        });

	});
	function displayOverlayDialog(layerId) {
		window.scroll(0,0);
		//$('#upgrade_btn').attr('disabled', true);
		$('#middle_panel').fadeTo('slow', 0.5);
		$('.middle').fadeTo('slow', 0.5);
		$('#' + layerId).show();
	}

	function hideOverlayDialog(layerId) {
		$('#' + layerId).hide();
		//$('#upgrade_btn').attr('disabled', false);
		$('#middle_panel').fadeTo('slow', 1);
		$('.middle').fadeTo('slow', 1);
	}
	
	function changeLocale(locale) {
    	$("#localeForm [name=locale]").val(locale);
    	$("#localeForm").submit();
	};

	initClock('April  1, 2016 16:58:33', 'dynamic_clock');
</script>

                        if (l.indexOf('#') !== -1 && l.indexOf('&_suid') !== -1) {
                            u = l.split('#')[1];
                            var pos = u.indexOf('&_suid');
                            u = u.substring(0, pos);
                            document.location.href = u;
                        }
                    })();

if(document.getElementById("noticeScroll")){
	var scrollup = new ScrollText("noticeScroll");
	scrollup.LineHeight = 24;        //åææå­æ»å¨çé«åº¦
	scrollup.Amount = 1;            //æ³¨æ:å­æ¨¡å(LineHeight)ä¸å®è¦è½æ´é¤Amount.
	scrollup.Delay = 20;           //å»¶æ¶
	scrollup.Start();             //æå­èªå¨æ»å¨
	scrollup.Direction = "up";   //é»è®¤è®¾ç½®ä¸ºæå­åä¸æ»å¨
}		
$(function(){
	$(window).on('scroll',function(){
		var st = $(document).scrollTop();
		if( st>0 ){
			if( $('#content').length != 0  ){
				var w = $(window).width(),mw = $('#content').width();
				if( (w-mw)/2 > 70 )
					$('#gotop').css({'left':(w-mw)/2+mw+20});
				else{
					$('#gotop').css({'left':'auto'});
				}
			}
			$('#gotop').fadeIn(function(){
				$(this).removeClass('hide');
			});
		}else{
			$('#gotop').fadeOut(function(){
				$(this).addClass('hide');
			});
		}	
	});
	$('#gotop .go').on('click',function(){
		$('html,body').animate({'scrollTop':0},500);
	});

	$('#gotop .cz-weixin').hover(function(){
		$('#gotop .cz-weixin-con').removeClass('hide');
	},function(){
		$('#gotop .cz-weixin-con').addClass('hide');
	});
});

	</script>
